# Reduces Docker build context (faster builds + smaller images).
# Anything not listed here is sent to the daemon and considered for the image.

# Build outputs / caches
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.vite
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.cache

# Test artifacts
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/screenshots
**/__diff_output__

# Dev infra
.git
.github
.cursor
.cursorrules
.vscode
.idea

# Supabase local
supabase/.temp
supabase/.branches
supabase/seed.sql

# Local environment & secrets — NEVER bake into the image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
# Exception: scanner's .env.production contains ONLY public values
# (Supabase URL + anon key + store_id) and MUST be baked into the build so
# Vite picks them up via import.meta.env.* at build time. Service-role keys
# never go here — see apps/scanner/.env.production for the inventory.
!apps/scanner/.env.production

# Logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# Misc
**/.DS_Store
**/tmp
**/temp
**/uploads
docs
README.md
*.md
!Dockerfile
actions.jsonl

# Pulled run evidence (P0-2, 2026-07-16) — local forensic copies from
# Supabase Storage / the worker. Never belongs in an image, and it was
# adding MBs to every build context upload.
rpa-captures
**/rpa-output
family-audit
sql
